a good candidate but unfortunately for the wrong party 
modrow has been premier since november when a new cabinet was 
seated following the ouster of hardline erich honecker and his top 
lieutenants most of whom are now under investigation for alleged 
corruption and misuse of office 
polls have predicted boehmes party will emerge with the biggest 
bloc of votes in the elections but it is unclear whether the 
